<i>noun</i>: 참혹 [참혹], 비참 [비ː참] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>참혹 [참혹]</dt><br>
<dd>wretchedness</dd><br>
<dd>매우 비참하고 끔찍함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being very miserable and feeling terrible.</dd><br>
<dt>비참 [비ː참]</dt><br>
<dd>misery; wretchedness; distress</dd><br>
<dd>견딜 수 없을 정도로 슬프고 끔찍함.</dd><br>
<dd>An unbearably sad and dreadful feeling.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>